</p>
<p>And <code>phpunit.xml.dist</code> also now lives in the root directory. That means no more
<code>phpunit -c app</code>: just run <code>phpunit</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">phpunit</div></code></pre>
<p>and it'll find the configuration file automatically.</p>
<p>That's it for the new directory structure, you can start using it right now, or leave
your project alone.</p>

    
